title: Ney Rosauro (Classical Marimba)
description:
Actually two discs into one.  The first is Concert No.2 For Marimba

1.Reflections and Dreams - 8:27

2.Walking on Clouds - 8:06

3.Water Running in High Mountain - 6:41


The next disc is the four movements of Marimba Concerto.  I think its a full orchestra, but who knows?

1.Greetings - 3:33

2.Lament - 6:41

3.Dance - 3:48

4.Farewell - 5:09


I believe, but am not sure, that most of these are performed by the University of Calgary or Miami ensembles.  Rosauro, i think, teaches at one >.<    


Ney Rosauro wrote both pieces and still composes for percussion.  I have played some and they aren't just awesome to listen too...they're equally fun.


His website is NeyRosauro.com  Please support artists and seed :D
